description: Welcome to Vantage Point, a professionally managed, 30-unit boutique building constructed in 2023. This home offers a perfect blend of modern finishes and thoughtful design. Upon entering, you're welcomed into a bright, open-concept living area featuring an eat-in kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, white shaker cabinetry, quartz countertops, and a spacious peninsula, ideal for both casual dining and entertaining. The living room provides ample space for a home office setup and offers direct access to a private patio, perfect for enjoying outdoor relaxation. The generously sized primary bedroom is filled with natural light and offers excellent closet space. The luxurious bathroom includes a double vanity and a fully tiled walk-in shower with glass enclosure. This move-in-ready home combines contemporary comfort with unbeatable convenience in one of South Boston’s most desirable locations. Additional features include a garage parking spot and additional bike storage!
